<Project>
  <PropertyGroup>
    <TargetFrameworks>net8.0;net10.0</TargetFrameworks>
    <LangVersion>preview</LangVersion>
    <Nullable>enable</Nullable>
    <ImplicitUsings>enable</ImplicitUsings>
    <InvariantGlobalization>false</InvariantGlobalization>
    <TreatWarningsAsErrors>true</TreatWarningsAsErrors>
    <Version>1.4.17</Version>
    <PackageReleaseNotes>
      Streaming breadth and correctness. The streamability analysis is now compositional (posture/sweep over the expression tree) rather than a fixed set of recognized shapes, so many more streamable constructs are accepted and executed as true streaming instead of falling back to whole-input buffering or empty output. Newly streamed correctly: xsl:apply-templates over a downward select (dispatching the matched template body per node, with tunnel and non-tunnel parameters); general comparisons over a per-item attribute-arithmetic tail such as (path/(@value*2)) = n; the absorbing/windowing functions head, tail, subsequence, remove, insert-before and sum's empty default; xsl:message and xsl:assert as grounding sinks; namespace-wildcard (*:name) selects; value-of / xsl:attribute atomization and separators over a streamed sequence; ancestor/climbing populations; and xsl:iterate over a grounded atomic crawl. Also corrects xsl:attribute simple-content node merging on the non-streaming path. Requires PhoenixmlDb.Core 1.2.0 and PhoenixmlDb.XQuery 1.5.2. No API changes. See RELEASES.md for full notes.
    </PackageReleaseNotes>
    <NoWarn>$(NoWarn);CS1591</NoWarn>
    <EnforceCodeStyleInBuild>true</EnforceCodeStyleInBuild>
    <AnalysisLevel>latest-all</AnalysisLevel>
  </PropertyGroup>

  <PropertyGroup>
    <Authors>Endpoint Systems</Authors>
    <Company>Endpoint Systems</Company>
    <Product>PhoenixmlDb</Product>
    <Copyright>Copyright © Endpoint Systems 2026. All rights reserved.</Copyright>
    <RepositoryType>git</RepositoryType>
    <RepositoryUrl>https://github.com/phoenixmldb/phoenixmldb-xslt</RepositoryUrl>
    <PackageProjectUrl>https://phoenixml.dev</PackageProjectUrl>
    <PackageLicenseExpression>Apache-2.0</PackageLicenseExpression>
    <PackageIcon>icon.png</PackageIcon>
    <PackageReadmeFile>PACKAGE.md</PackageReadmeFile>
    <GenerateDocumentationFile>true</GenerateDocumentationFile>
  </PropertyGroup>

  <ItemGroup>
    <None Include="$(MSBuildThisFileDirectory)icon.png" Pack="true" PackagePath="" />
    <None Include="$(MSBuildThisFileDirectory)PACKAGE.md" Pack="true" PackagePath="" />
  </ItemGroup>

  <PropertyGroup Condition="'$(Configuration)' == 'Release'">
    <DebugType>embedded</DebugType>
    <DebugSymbols>true</DebugSymbols>
    <Deterministic>true</Deterministic>
  </PropertyGroup>
</Project>
